<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Tutorials on Personal Blogs for Fernweh</title><link>https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/categories/tutorials/</link><description>Recent content in Tutorials on Personal Blogs for Fernweh</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Sep 2025 16:40:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/categories/tutorials/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>How to Download and Install Python</title><link>https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Sep 2025 16:40:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/banner.jpg" alt="Featured image of post How to Download and Install Python" /&gt;&lt;h1 id="how-to-download-and-install-python"&gt;How to Download and Install Python
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Python is an interpreted, high-level and general-purpose programming language. Python’s design philosophy emphasizes
code readability with its notable use of significant whitespace. This article will serve as an informative guide and
give you a clear understanding of how to set up a Python environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="download-python-installation-packages"&gt;Download Python Installation Packages
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.python.org/downloads/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Python official website&lt;/a&gt; provides various versions of Python installation packages
for selection. Of course, considering that the speed of connecting to the Python official website in somewhere may be
slow, I recommend using a mirror site to download the Python installation package.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://mirrors.aliyun.com/python-release/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Alibaba Mirror Site&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/python/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;USTC Mirror Site&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;hellip;..&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you know of other mirror sites, please &lt;a class="link" href="mailto:libochen@codeglimpse.top" &gt;contact me&lt;/a&gt; to update them!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="python-installation"&gt;Python installation
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="windows"&gt;Windows
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4 id="the-simplest-manual-installation"&gt;The Simplest Manual Installation
&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run the installer and select the following two options:
The first option installs Python with administrator privileges.
The second option automatically adds Python to your system environment path (highly recommended).
&lt;img src="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/1.png"
width="999"
height="615"
srcset="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/1_hu_f4f49cd52bd194d9.png 480w, https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/1_hu_d76b93e57f9064ed.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Install Page"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="162"
data-flex-basis="389px"
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Click &lt;strong&gt;Install Now&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Click &lt;strong&gt;Close&lt;/strong&gt; , Installation complete!
&lt;img src="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/2.png"
width="999"
height="615"
srcset="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/2_hu_4c105e39875b064c.png 480w, https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/2_hu_e884941f78a09995.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Install Complete"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="162"
data-flex-basis="389px"
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h5 id="customize-installation"&gt;Customize installation
&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run the installer, still recommended to select the following two options:
&lt;img src="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/1.png"
width="999"
height="615"
srcset="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/1_hu_f4f49cd52bd194d9.png 480w, https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/1_hu_d76b93e57f9064ed.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Install Page"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="162"
data-flex-basis="389px"
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Click &lt;strong&gt;Customize installation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Choose optional features as needed:
&lt;img src="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/3.png"
width="999"
height="615"
srcset="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/3_hu_2f19553966b84280.png 480w, https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/3_hu_e33c702d7268a9f5.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Optional Features"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="162"
data-flex-basis="389px"
&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Documentation: Documentation and help files for installing Python. Select this option only needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;pip: Python package management tool. Very important, must choose&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;tcl/tk and IDLE: tcl/tk and IDLE are two graphical user interfaces, IDLE is Integrated Development Environment and
Learning，a python IDE that comes with it. However, we recommend using Pycharm as an IDE for learning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Python test suite: Provides a set of test suites for testing Python interpreters and standard libraries. Although
beginners generally do not need to use it, this kit is still very useful, it is recommended to choose it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;py launcher: Ensure user starts python using python commands in the command line&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;for all users（requires admin privileges）: Ask if choose &amp;lsquo;py launcher&amp;rsquo; for all users on the computer. Recommended
to choose&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Click &lt;strong&gt;Next&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Choose advanced option as needed:
&lt;img src="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/4.png"
width="999"
height="615"
srcset="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/4_hu_5c30d0f6e8c1b4d3.png 480w, https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/4_hu_a74ac4ce209f42e4.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Advanced options"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="162"
data-flex-basis="389px"
&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install Python 3.12 for all users: Generally has no effect on use, but still recommended to choose it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Associate files with Python (requires the &amp;lsquo;py&amp;rsquo; launcher): Enable the system to automatically associate Python with
specific file types. When double click Python script files in File Explorer, the system will automatically use the
Python interpreter to run these scripts. This can be chosen as needed, but usually the file will be associated
with Pycharm later on&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create shortcuts for installed applications: Create desktop shortcuts. Generally, there is no need to choose&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add Python to environment variables: Selecting this option adds the path to the Python interpreter to the system&amp;rsquo;s
environment variables, so that the Python interpreter can be run directly from the command line without having to
enter the full path. Recommended to choose&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Precompile standard library: Pre-compiled the Python standard library to improve the import speed of standard
library modules. This can be chosen or not&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Download debugging symbols: Debug symbols for developers and debuggers. Choose only need&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Download debug binaries (requires VS 2017 or later): A binary file for debug versions for developers and
debuggers. Choose only need&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Select the directory for installation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Click &lt;strong&gt;Install&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Click &lt;strong&gt;Close&lt;/strong&gt; , Complete the installation
&lt;img src="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/2.png"
width="999"
height="615"
srcset="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/2_hu_4c105e39875b064c.png 480w, https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/2_hu_e884941f78a09995.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Install Complete"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="162"
data-flex-basis="389px"
&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h4 id="the-simplest-silent-installationautomatic-installation"&gt;The Simplest silent installation/automatic installation
&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Find the installation package, right-click &lt;strong&gt;Properties&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Record the &lt;strong&gt;File Name&lt;/strong&gt; and the installation package path in the &lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;.
&lt;img src="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/5.png"
width="403"
height="540"
srcset="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/5_hu_800c639d74df1bdb.png 480w, https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/5_hu_fe772c5ff7d960cf.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="Properties"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="74"
data-flex-basis="179px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Type &lt;code&gt;cmd&lt;/code&gt; in the bottom-left corner of the desktop to open the command prompt as an administrator
&lt;img src="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/6.png"
width="781"
height="681"
srcset="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/6_hu_e0c69f214929979b.png 480w, https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/6_hu_47f37bf1d3f13915.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="cmd"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="114"
data-flex-basis="275px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enter the following commands in sequence:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bat" data-lang="bat"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; C:\Users\user\Desktop
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;python-3.13.7-amd64.exe /quiet InstallAllUsers=1 PrependPath=1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Attention: &lt;br&gt;
  Replace C:\Users\user\Desktop with the installation package path from Step 2.&lt;br&gt;
  Replace python-3.13.7-amd64.exe with the filename from Step 2. (don&amp;rsquo;t forget the .exe)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/7.png"
width="976"
height="510"
srcset="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/7_hu_5b9019b91b2324bf.png 480w, https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/7_hu_471650c200671600.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="install"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="191"
data-flex-basis="459px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After waiting a few minutes, check in the Start menu to see if the installation is complete.
&lt;img src="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/8.png"
width="754"
height="694"
srcset="https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/8_hu_bf33e7da52b99614.png 480w, https://blog.codeglimpse.top/en/p/python-install/8_hu_11bd7f9731c5682c.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="check"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="108"
data-flex-basis="260px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h5 id="custom-script-installation"&gt;Custom Script Installation
&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create a new text file and name it as &lt;code&gt;unattend.xml&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fill in the content:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt; 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt; 2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt; 3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt; 4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt; 5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt; 6
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt; 7
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt; 8
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt; 9
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;10
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;11
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;12
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;13
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;14
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;15
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;16
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;17
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;18
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;19
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;20
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;21
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;22
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;23
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;24
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;25
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;26
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;27
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Options&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;InstallAllUsers&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;TargetDir&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;C:\Python313&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;DefaultAllUsersTargetDir&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;C:\Python313&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;DefaultJustForMeTargetDir&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;C:\Python313&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;DefaultCustomTargetDir&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;C:\Python313&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;AssociateFiles&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;CompileAll&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;PrependPath&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;AppendPath&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;0&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;Shortcuts&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;Include_doc&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;Include_debug&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;Include_dev&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;Include_exe&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;Option&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;Include_launcher&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Value=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
